{"tid":1835894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"往武漢高鐵乘客退票　不滿只退回不足一半車費","createTime":"2020-01-23T04:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T04:35:19.000Z","uid":26650,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"57227ef9b00cdfa41df538926a9cd574dc78879f","tid":1835894,"uid":26650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:18:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504384-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504384-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=0979fea2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504384-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ee7e0472\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504384-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n在高鐵西九龍站，有多名買了前往湖北武漢高鐵票的乘客退票。<br />\n<br />\n原本買年初一高鐵票到湖北探望父母的王小姐表示，農曆新年打算回鄉，但父母擔心她受感染，勸她不要回鄉。她說，她買了超過1千元的高鐵票，不滿只能退回不足一半的車費，形容「很淒涼」，表示一定會投訴。<br />\n<br />\n另外，買了明日的高鐵票回武漢的鄧小姐表示，打算回鄉探親，武漢市交通停運，猶如「封城」，但年初五要上班，擔心到時沒有交通工具回港，所以退票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1549640887c4675ee6ebe7c3f418b1159b87c3","tid":1835894,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"黨鐵咁衰？大陸鐵路局係免費退票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b413b41dd42bd726f3da78ce3418c2d68257f15","tid":1835894,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"到湖北探望父母的王小姐表示，農曆新年打算回鄉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港真係好撚多支那人"},{"pid":"7a3e34d6378b617849bd6c68871e45273bacb268","tid":1835894,"uid":121937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:35:19.000Z","msg":"我驚到真係比你去果時都唔夠膽去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}